article_title: Harvard Study Of CBO Reports Says Nothing New Or Interesting About King v. Burwell

article_metadata.author: Michael F. Cannon

og.description: Skocpol's study is just the latest in a series of silly and desperate attempts to bolster the government's untenable position in King v. Burwell. The law is clear, and the government is on the wrong side of it.
